summary: This email chain is a  representation of a customer inquiry about a used car from the webstore wheels4cashcom It covers various stages of the customers inquiry from initial interest to scheduling a test drive and demonstrates the webstores customer support responses

This email chain continues the  customer inquiry about financing options for a used car from wheels4cashcom It covers the customers questions about financing details the application process and document submission The webstores support team provides information and guidance throughout the process

This email chain continues the  customer inquiry about a used car from wheels4cashcom The customer requests the maintenance history of the vehicle and the webstores support team responds by explaining their process to obtain the information and subsequently provides the maintenance history to the customer
